---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Roadmap"
  description="A practical roadmap for shaping CodeArmy into a focused product."
>
  <section class="container page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Roadmap</p>
    <h1>Ship a focused product before a broad platform.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      CodeArmy should start as a clear, narrow product for long-running AI coding and research
      campaigns. Breadth comes later.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="container page-body grid-3">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>v0.1</h3>
      <p>Trae-first product package.</p>
      <ul class="page-list">
        <li>Landing page and docs</li>
        <li>Campaign lifecycle narrative</li>
        <li>Trae integration path</li>
        <li>Quickstart and current runtime repo links</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>v0.2</h3>
      <p>Operational bundle.</p>
      <ul class="page-list">
        <li>CodeArmy CLI</li>
        <li>MCP server for Trae Solo</li>
        <li>Custom agents and Skills pack</li>
        <li>Research case studies</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>v0.3</h3>
      <p>Team workflow expansion.</p>
      <ul class="page-list">
        <li>Feishu sync</li>
        <li>Approval/reporting polish</li>
        <li>More durable docs and examples</li>
        <li>Optional custom domain</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
